Package: afratzscherFunctions
Title: Split Data into Training and Test Data for Machine Learning
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Anne-Sophie", 
           family = "Fratzscher", 
           email = "afratz@student.ubc.ca", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
  This package provides a function to split data in a tibble or dataframe into 
  training and test data for machine learning. There are options to specify the 
  train-test split ratio and to shuffle the data prior to splitting. 
